<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
In this usage <strong>@HI{{yori}}</strong> is a particle which indicates a set point in time or space.

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KT{{mekishiko}}ha@KJ{{red^road-way}}<strong>yori</strong>@KJ{{north}}niarimasu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Mexico is located north of the equator.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{three^time}}<strong>yori</strong>@KJ{{in*front}}ni@KJ{{come}}tekudasai.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Please come back before three o'clock.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>
</p>

